title: "Agentic AI for 3GPP-Compliant Adaptive Resource Allocation in 5G NR Satellite Networks"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-04-04
url: "https://github.com/senthilv83/Agentic-RAN"
keywords:
  - 5G NR
  - Satellite Networks
  - Agentic AI
  - 3GPP TS 23.501
  - Resource Allocation
  - LangChain
  - Machine Learning
abstract: "An Agentic AI-driven framework for real-time, edge-level adaptive resource allocation in 5G NR Satellite Networks. This framework utilizes a multi-stage reasoning architecture powered by Machine Learning (Random Forest, K-Means) and Large Language Models (LLMs) via LangChain to provide explainable, policy-compliant resource allocation strategies."
